		</tr><tr>
			<td><a href="FeatDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Amplified Rage"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Amplified Rage</a></td><td>Half-orc or orc, rage class feature</td><td>Make your rage more powerful when near others raging</td>
		</tr><tr style="background-color:#CCCCCC;">
