		</tr><tr>
			<td><a href="FeatDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Assisted Ascension"><img src="images\PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif" title="PFS Legal" style="margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;"> Assisted Ascension</a></td><td>Climb 5 ranks</td><td>Climb with allies more effectively</td>
		</tr><tr style="background-color:#CCCCCC;">
